      "writtenOn": "2016-11-28T18:25:11Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Good catch, thank you.  I expanded this to break if we are past that value of interest, which should keep unnecessary reads at bay.\nAdded test to make sure this edgecase is covered. More tests to be added in next CL.",
      "parentUuid": "4df48341_4d7f58ca",
      "revId": "c9809743d5fb55cba6369600438261c48fdf39e5",
      "serverId": "5086850b-e599-37d2-8ec8-ff16aeccbf02",
